<b>."},{"content":"When beans are tender, drain and reserve cooking liquid."},{"content":"Add cooked beans and up to 375 g cooking liquid (no higher than maximum mark in mixing bowl). Replace measuring cup with simmering basket and simmer <b>20-30 min\/98°C\/\/speed <b> until beans have thickened the sauce. Adjust seasoning and serve with grilled meats."}],"hintsAndTricks":["While cooking the beans on the hob, add extra water if necessary to keep them covered.","Cool leftovers to room temperature then place in an airtight container. Refrigerate for up to 1 week, or freeze for a month."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","2h 30m","8 portions"]}